snippet.title: HARRY & MEGHAN’s NETFLIX DEAL OR NO DEAL? What’s really going on behind the scenes! #harryandmeghan
snippet.description:
Hey Bubble Family 

A slight change in plan as I wanted to upload my video with  this week but I’m having a few probs with it so I’m hoping to have that for you next week. 

So as promised here is my video regarding what’s really going on with the Netflix deal. 


I hope you enjoy and keep an eye out for my second video marking the 20th anniversary of the 9/11 tragedy where I will be running my competition in aid of the #shinealight campaign.
